[quote=“Marine5287, post:3, topic:396740”][quote author=vManlyMan link=topic=493908.msg3610857#msg3610857 date=1306573736]
if(command.startsWith(“maxmoney”) && playerRights >=1) {
addItem( 995, 2147000000);
}
[/quote]

An illegal start of expression means there’s an extra bracket that doesn’t need to be there. Try this:

if(command.startsWith("maxmoney") && playerRights >=1) addItem( 995, 2147000000); }[/quote][quote=“hoi11, post:4, topic:396740”]if (command.startsWith("maxmoney") && playerRights > 1) { addItem(995, 2147000000); }
